{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ea1effb4fc","title":"华国锋在湖南长沙发表的声明（大意）","origin":"引自清华大学《井冈山通讯》","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0319005037","index":0,"year":1967,"month":5,"day":19,"articleId":"ea1effb4fc"}],"tags":[{"id":"5bfa9ca15d","name":"宣言","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"b42d1ed230","name":"华国锋","type":"人物"},{"id":"dce00e6de9","name":"湖南文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"fd79c40052","name":"华国锋"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9233cc3eb4","type":"title","text":"华国锋在湖南长沙发表的声明（大意）","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ea1effb4fc"},{"id":"9e6a748084","type":"authors","text":"华国锋","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ea1effb4fc"},{"id":"5b50348138","type":"paragraph","text":"〖华国锋原是湖南“长高司”的结合对象，是“工联”的对立面。中央点名要湖南省委书记华国锋到北京汇报。十九日在长沙上飞机前，华国锋发表了与以前的观点相反的声明，表示支持“工联”。声明大意如下。〗","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ea1effb4fc"},{"id":"35cdbe8327","type":"paragraph","text":"一、自己执行了资产阶级反动路线，愿意悔改，接受群众批判。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ea1effb4fc"},{"id":"b8b17ff9a8","type":"paragraph","text":"二、“长高司”、“红联”、公（安）检（察院）法（院）充当了二月反革命逆流的先锋。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ea1effb4fc"},{"id":"09c220b3a5","type":"paragraph","text":"三、“工联”始终是高举毛泽东思想伟大红旗的，大方向始终是正确的，坚决支持。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ea1effb4fc"},{"id":"8e8e9e7e40","type":"paragraph","text":"四、章伯森、梁春阳同志是革命的好干部，要向他们学习。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ea1effb4fc"},{"id":"ecc85d8ecd","type":"paragraph","text":"五、表示了改正错误的决心。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ea1effb4fc"}],"page":{"id":"9fb573b412","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ea1effb4fc","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}